{"article_id":"PYBdgANveDrGJv1M","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FERGUSON , Mo . -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Armored vehicles , riot gear , tear gas and looting returned to this small Midwest city early Saturday","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"as a brief period of peaceful demonstrations gave way to a violent atmosphere of anarchy .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"The intense night shattered a short-lived calm","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that had been hailed as a turning point after a week of protests","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"following the fatal shooting of Michael Brown , a black unarmed 18-year-old","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"killed by a police officer .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"During the night , buildings burned ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"windows shattered ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and chaos ensued","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"as protesters stood in the street","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"criticizing police .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Officers threatened to arrest protesters","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"who came near their trucks .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Yet authorities did not attempt to stop any looting","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"as citizens moved","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to protect local businesses from sporadic thefts .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"`` We did n't have any supervision","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"so people got super out of hand , ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"said Derrick Robinson , 30 , of Ferguson .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"`` I was very disappointed and upset about what was going on . ''","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Friday evening 's protests were calm , though boisterous .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"People played drums and sang songs in memory of Brown at QuikTrip ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"where protesters have gathered for the last week .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"However , around midnight Saturday , protesters began clashing with police officers","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"as cops in armored vehicles lined up on West Florissant Avenue , a main city thoroughfare .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"As the mood intensified ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"officers threw tear gas into the crowd","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and then quickly retreated .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"But some 30 minutes later , the officers returned to a position on the street","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that they would occupy for the next four to five hours .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"On Friday , officials released the name of the officer","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"who killed Brown","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"- Darren Wilson -","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"as well as information","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that Brown was a suspect in a robbery .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"The move","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"- to name Brown 's killer","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"while also releasing information about a possible criminal act by the teen -","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"angered many protesters","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"who repeatedly said","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"they thought","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"police were trying to paint Brown as a criminal","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"deserving of death .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Anthony Shahid , one of the most visible activists","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"who has been protesting in Ferguson ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"he sensed","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"things would escalate","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"as soon as he learned about the information","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"police released .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"`` They","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"( Ferguson Police )","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"gave a press conference","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"and one of the first things","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"they did","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"was read about this man 's history , ''","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"`` It inflamed this community .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"All","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"you heard people say","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"was that they did n't like that .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"it 's very disrespectful , insensitive and callous . ''","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"In a now-familiar scene in Ferguson , police officers Saturday morning held rifles","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and yelled at protesters to get out of the street","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"or risk being arrested .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Despite this , some in the crowd walked toward police officers with their hands in the air .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Eventually other protesters convinced people","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"walking toward the officers","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"to move back .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"It was then ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"as people walked back ,","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"that some began breaking into nearby stores .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"At a nearby Beauty Supply Store , people stole bags of fake hair ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"while across the street at Ferguson Market and Liquor others carried out large bottles of alcohol .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"Ferguson Market and Liquor is the store","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"that","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"Ferguson police say","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"Brown is suspected of robbing shortly before his death .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"On Saturday morning , looters smashed its front door","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and ransacked its shelves .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"The chaos caught Robinson off guard .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"The Ferguson resident said","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"he had been protesting since 9 a.m. Friday","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"and left the demonstration area at about midnight Saturday .","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"`` I got call at about 1:30 a.m.","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"saying","depth":17},{"id":88,"text":"they are looting","depth":18},{"id":89,"text":"and breaking into people 's stores","depth":19},{"id":90,"text":"and that the goal is to burn down Ferguson Market , ''","depth":19},{"id":91,"text":"Robinson said .","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"`` I immediately came back","depth":16},{"id":93,"text":"to really see what was happening .","depth":16},{"id":94,"text":"I was very disappointed and upset about what was going on . ''","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"Robinson 's disappointment motivated him to help fend off looters from vulnerable stores .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Others like him pleaded with looters to stop taking merchandise","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"while police silently watched .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Christopher Scott , 24 , of Northwoods , Mo. , stood in front of Ferguson Market and Liquor ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"blocking the door 's shattered front glass door","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"and sharing his feelings with looters .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"He , along with about 10 other men , physically pushed back a crowd of young men","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"who were trying to make their way into the convenience store .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"`` I just told them","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"that they need to think , ''","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"Scott said .","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"`` We are smarter than that .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"I told them","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"that we live here ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"we sleep here ,","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"we eat in our community","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"so it does n't make sense for us to turn on our community . ''","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"He added :","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"`` I do n't want the message sent","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"that everyone out here is just looting ,","depth":16},{"id":115,"text":"robbing","depth":17},{"id":116,"text":"and stealing .","depth":17},{"id":117,"text":"That 's not the case .","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"A lot of us want justice .","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"A lot of us want peace .","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"A lot of us want a well-regulated community .","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"It 's not right for us to tear down our own community .","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"If anything we need to be building it up . ''","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Amid the chaos , a stark distinction emerged between protesters","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"who blocked people from breaking into stores","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"and looters","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"who hastily carried items away .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"Despite the residents","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"who acted as peacekeepers ,","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"Ferguson eventually became the scene of multiple robberies","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"as people went from store to store","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"carrying out stolen goods .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"DaVhaun Coleman , 21 , of Florissant , Mo. , held a canister of tear gas in his hand","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"as he explained","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that he was angry","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"police were trying to paint Brown as a criminal .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"that he thought","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"police Saturday used tear gas on the crowd unnecessarily .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"`` They want to get hands-on , ''","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Coleman said of police .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"`` They are just doing what they were trained to do . ''","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"Missouri State Highway Patrol Captain Ron Johnson said","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"some in the crowd began throwing rocks and other objects at police ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"but no arrests were made .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"One officer was hurt ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"but information on his injuries was not immediately available .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"No protesters were hurt .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"Brown 's family had urged protesters to remain nonviolent","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"hours before chaos broke out again .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"In a Friday afternoon press conference , Ferguson , Mo . Police Chief Thomas Jackson said","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"Wilson did not initially make a connection between the robbery and Brown .","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"Wilson stopped Brown and a friend","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"because `` they were in the middle of the street ,","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"blocking traffic , ''","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Jackson said .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"Hours later , however , Jackson told a slightly different story to CNN and NBC ,","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"that Wilson noticed Brown was carrying a box of cigars","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"that had been reported stolen .","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"Wilson ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"initially stopped Brown","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"for blocking traffic ,","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"but","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"as he began driving past Brown ,","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"he noticed","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"Brown was holding cigars .","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"At that point , Wilson `` made the connection ''","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"that Brown might have been involved in a theft","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"that had just been broadcast on police radio ,","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Jackson said .","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"Jackson would not say","depth":5},{"id":173,"text":"why he released the information","depth":6},{"id":174,"text":"when he did the way","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"he did ,","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"other than to say","depth":5},{"id":177,"text":"he was responding to freedom of information requests from the public about the robbery .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":355,"left":0,"right":354,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":354,"left":326,"right":353,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":326,"left":207,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":197,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":193,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":183,"right":192,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":179,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":180,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":187,"right":191,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":7,"right":184,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":188,"right":190,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":14,"right":189,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":195,"right":20,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":194,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":199,"right":205,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":21,"rig